{"tid":509863,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"女性主義組織到梵蒂岡示威　無上裝女子圖搶奪「耶穌」","createTime":"2017-12-25T18:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-26T05:31:54.000Z","uid":68476,"like":96,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"d0628ea44d5cb6afdc7d548770b494008713b28e","tid":509863,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T18:59:33.000Z","msg":"女性主義組織到梵蒂岡示威　無上裝女子圖搶奪「耶穌」<br />\n<br />\n在梵蒂岡聖伯多祿廣場，有女性主義運動團體到場示威，一名上身裸露的示威者越過分隔線，企圖搶走聖誕場景中的耶穌嬰兒塑像，遭到警方制止，她當時高呼口號，身上寫上「上帝是女性」的示威字句，她被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n事件發生在教宗方濟各發表聖誕文告前大約2小時。女性主義運動團體「費曼」在官方網站表示，被捕者是他們的成員，是一名「性別極端分子」。這個組織在烏克蘭成立，以「打倒父權」為目標。"},{"pid":"9c56e06fadacc52a2874ea607246d76e064df785","tid":509863,"uid":91519,"like":113,"dislike":2,"score":111,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T19:03:14.000Z","msg":"耶撚大戰女權閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75303bfc2c6e4a85d8503a71942046d9414f92ac","tid":509863,"uid":64884,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T19:04:29.000Z","msg":"做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"764a82a82a0c2e116b9c48bde338eff16a7f52d1","tid":509863,"uid":64601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T20:41:38.000Z","msg":"圖呢"},{"pid":"eb0b3e86acb39b3deda7ca476ca2ce3532205568","tid":509863,"uid":37666,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T21:58:21.000Z","msg":"哇 精彩啦今次<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7662797834a22d4cde5b1c7d7e1d1cf5bffa9dc","tid":509863,"uid":82845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T22:00:01.000Z","msg":"冇圖講乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aeae384e97b0b02f4a3f3cdf15828a7c781dc47","tid":509863,"uid":3773,"like":91,"dislike":1,"score":90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-25T22:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.wehuntedthemammoth.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/tomatomeme.jpg\" data-thumbna